  ('judicial-7b850ce6-moex-00075', 'judicial-7b850ce6', 'judicial-7b850ce6-moex-110-8d1d3a67', 'sub-judicial-7b850ce6-01', NULL, 'essay', '某珠寶店發生搶案，有不知名路人對珠寶店老闆甲說：「我看到歹徒
